PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Agriculture and Agri-Food of DORIS ARMITAGE PRIDDLE of Toronto, Ontario, to be a director of the Board of Directors of Farm Credit Canada to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, effective November 26, 2012, in the place of Carl Spencer.
